        "legenda": "Second citizenship used to be about opportunity. Today, it's increasingly about resilience.\nJoe Rice, our Head of Citizenship Programs, has spent years working closely with private clients navigating these decisions - and the shift he's observed is clear. People aren't seeking a second passport because they're planning to leave. They're seeking it because they want the option to, if they ever need to.\nㅤ\nThat distinction matters. And it's reshaping how globally mobile individuals think about their futures.\nㅤ\n🔍 Read the full piece via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#SecondPassport #CitizenshipByInvestment #PlanB #GlobalMobility #InvestmentMigration #WealthStrategy #ResidencyPlanning #CitizenshipPlanning #HNWIInvesting #JurisdictionalDiversification #GlobalCitizenSolutions #Optionality #WealthProtection #FamilyPlanning #ExpatLife #GlobalCitizen #ThoughtLeadership",
