        "legenda": "If you've been thinking about a second passport or residency, this is the session to attend.\nOur panel of five specialists will walk through the Caribbean programs, Europe's Golden Visa landscape in 2026, and how to structure the right Plan B based on your specific situation - budget, timeline, family, and tax position.\nThis is a free, no-fluff briefing designed for investors who are ready to make informed decisions.\n🔍 Register for free: link in bio.\nㅤ\n#PlanB #SecondPassport #GoldenVisa #ResidencyByInvestment #CitizenshipByInvestment #GlobalMobility #InvestmentMigration #WealthProtection #AmericansAbroad #HNWIInvesting #CaribbeanCitizenship #EuropeanResidency #Portugal #Italy #Greece #GlobalCitizenSolutions #Webinar",
