        "legenda": "The reasons are straightforward: lower cost of living, better healthcare, remote work flexibility, and tax environments that work in their favor. The barriers to moving have never been lower. What's needed is a clear plan.\nOur 2026 guide covers everything: the right visa for your situation, the best countries for Americans, what your US tax obligations look like abroad, and what the move actually costs from start to finish.\nㅤ\n🔍 Get the full guide via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#MoveAbroad #AmericansAbroad #ExpatLife #HowToMoveAbroad #GoldenVisa #DigitalNomad #RemoteWork #MoveToPortugal #MoveToSpain #MoveToEurope #Expat #GlobalMobility #ResidencyByInvestment #PlanBStrategy #TaxStrategy #GlobalCitizenSolutions #MovingAbroad2026 #AmericanExpat",
