    "ultimos_15_posts": [
      {
        "legenda": "Here’s a mistake many investors make with Golden Visas 👇\nㅤ\nThey choose a fund based only on the minimum investment.\n€500,000 is €500,000… right?\nㅤ\nNot exactly.\nㅤ\nTwo funds under the Portugal Golden Visa can look identical — but deliver very different results.\nㅤ\nWhy?\n💸 Fees\n📊 Strategy\n🔒 Lock-up periods\nㅤ\nSome funds charge more upfront.\nOthers take a bigger share of profits.\nSome lock your money in longer than expected.\nㅤ\nIt adds up fast.\nㅤ\nThe smarter move? Compare the details — not just the price tag.\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisa #Portugal #InvestmentFunds #WealthStrategy #EUResidency #InvestmentMigration #SmartInvesting",
        "curtidas": 2,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "Caribbean citizenship by investment is evolving and the change is significant for anyone holding or considering a second passport.\nFor investors, this means thinking differently about what citizenship is for: a relationship worth building.\nㅤ\n🔍 Read the full piece via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#CaribbeanCitizenship #CitizenshipByInvestment #StKittsAndNevis #SecondPassport #InvestmentMigration #GlobalMobility #CBI #PlanB #WealthStrategy #GenuineLink #PassportPlanning #HNWIInvesting #GlobalCitizenSolutions #WealthProtection #JurisdictionalDiversification #CitizenshipPlanning #PassportStrategy",
        "curtidas": 11,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "carrossel"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "There’s one detail that can change everything when choosing a Golden Visa.\nㅤ\nIt’s not the price.\nIt’s not the country.\nIt’s whether you actually need to live there.\nㅤ\nSome programs require real presence. Others don’t.\n🇵🇹 Portugal → ~7 days per year\n🇮🇹 Italy → no minimum stay\nㅤ\nThat one difference can completely reshape your lifestyle and freedom.\nThe real question is: what fits your plan?\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisa #Portugal #Italy #InvestmentMigration #EUResidency #MoveAbroad #GlobalCitizenship #WealthStrategy",
        "curtidas": 5,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "Most people compare Golden Visas the wrong way.\nThey focus on price… instead of strategy.\nㅤ\n🇬🇷 Greece looks cheap\n🇲🇹 Malta looks expensive\n🇵🇹 Portugal plays the long game\nㅤ\nBut here’s the truth: they’re built for completely different goals.\nㅤ\nThe right question isn’t “What’s cheaper?”\nIt’s “What fits my strategy?”\nㅤ\nBecause the best Golden Visa isn’t the cheapest one — it’s the one aligned with your future.\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisa #Portugal #Greece #Malta #InvestmentMigration #GlobalCitizenship #MoveAbroad #EUResidency #WealthStrategy",
        "curtidas": 10,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "A record 180,000 Americans moved abroad in 2025 - and the number keeps rising. Lower costs, better healthcare, tax efficiency, and lifestyle are all driving the shift.\nㅤ\nBut the best country for you depends entirely on your profile. A retiree, a remote worker, a family, and a high-net-worth investor each have a different answer. Our 2026 guide covers all 23 destinations in detail - from European favourites like Portugal and Spain to Caribbean citizenship programs and Asia-Pacific options like Singapore and New Zealand.\nㅤ\nWhatever your motivation, there's a smarter way to make the move.\nㅤ\n🔍 Explore the full guide via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#AmericansAbroad #MoveAbroad #BestCountriesToLiveIn #ExpatLife #GoldenVisa #CitizenshipByInvestment #MoveToPortugal #MoveToSpain #CaribbeanCBI #GlobalMobility #ResidencyByInvestment #TaxOptimization #DigitalNomad #MoveToEurope #SecondPassport #GlobalCitizenSolutions #AmericanExpat #PlanB2026",
        "curtidas": 8,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "carrossel"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "Think all Golden Visas in Europe are the same? Not anymore.\nㅤ\nIn just a few years:\nSpain shut down\nPortugal removed real estate\nGreece surged in popularity\nMalta and Italy became more strategic plays\nㅤ\nEach program now targets a different type of investor.\nㅤ\nSo the real question is: which one fits your goals?\nㅤ\nTalk to our experts:\nhttps://vist.ly/533nb\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisaEurope #ResidencyByInvestment #GlobalCitizen #InvestSmart #PortugalGoldenVisa #GreeceGoldenVisa #Malta #ItalyInvestorVisa #WealthPlanning",
        "curtidas": 7,
        "comentarios": 3,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "Second citizenship used to be about opportunity. Today, it's increasingly about resilience.\nJoe Rice, our Head of Citizenship Programs, has spent years working closely with private clients navigating these decisions - and the shift he's observed is clear. People aren't seeking a second passport because they're planning to leave. They're seeking it because they want the option to, if they ever need to.\nㅤ\nThat distinction matters. And it's reshaping how globally mobile individuals think about their futures.\nㅤ\n🔍 Read the full piece via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#SecondPassport #CitizenshipByInvestment #PlanB #GlobalMobility #InvestmentMigration #WealthStrategy #ResidencyPlanning #CitizenshipPlanning #HNWIInvesting #JurisdictionalDiversification #GlobalCitizenSolutions #Optionality #WealthProtection #FamilyPlanning #ExpatLife #GlobalCitizen #ThoughtLeadership",
        "curtidas": 19,
